Component ..> PostgreSQL : persist
Template ..> PostgreSQL : persist
Project ..> PostgreSQL : persist
DataSource ..> PostgreSQL : persist
DataMapping ..> PostgreSQL : persist
User ..> PostgreSQL : persist
HistoryRecord ..> PostgreSQL : persist
PageSchema ..> ObjectStorage : files
JsonDataTemplate ..> PostgreSQL : persist (opt)
ChartConfig ..> PostgreSQL : persist (opt)
TableColumn ..> PostgreSQL : persist (opt)
PaginationConfig ..> PostgreSQL : persist (opt)
TreeNode ..> PostgreSQL : persist (opt)

Component ..> Redis : cache
Project ..> Redis : cache
Project ..> ObjectStorage : files
PageSchema ..> Redis : cache

Component ..> LocalStorage : temp cache
Project ..> LocalStorage : temp cache
User ..> LocalStorage : prefs

ComponentEditFlow --> PostgreSQL : persist
ComponentEditFlow --> Redis : cache refresh

DataBindingFlow --> DataSource : uses
DataBindingFlow --> DataMapping : uses
DataBindingFlow --> Component : bind

JsonQuickInputFlow --> JsonDataTemplate : uses
JsonQuickInputFlow --> DataSource : create
JsonQuickInputFlow --> Component : update props

CollaborationFlow --> Redis : messaging
CollaborationFlow --> PostgreSQL : state persist

CodeGenFlow --> Project : read
CodeGenFlow --> Component : read
CodeGenFlow --> ObjectStorage : store

SchemaExportFlow --> Project : read
SchemaExportFlow --> Component : read
SchemaExportFlow --> DataSource : read
SchemaExportFlow --> ThemeConfig : read
SchemaExportFlow --> PageSchema : create
SchemaExportFlow --> ObjectStorage : store

SchemaImportFlow --> PageSchema : read
SchemaImportFlow --> ValidateSchemaVersion : uses
SchemaImportFlow --> MigrateOldSchema : uses
SchemaImportFlow --> ConvertToProjectData : uses
SchemaImportFlow --> Project : create
SchemaImportFlow --> Component : create
SchemaImportFlow --> DataSource : create
SchemaImportFlow --> ThemeConfig : create
SchemaImportFlow --> Redis : state update

DataParseFlow --> DataSource : upsert
DataMappingFlow --> DataMapping : create/use
LayoutFlow --> Component : move

JsonQuickInputFlow --> JsonDataTemplate : uses
JsonQuickInputFlow --> DataSource : create
JsonQuickInputFlow --> Component : update props

LocalStorageFlow --> LocalStorage : R/W
LocalStorageFlow --> TempDataCache : temp
LocalStorageFlow --> UserPreferencesStorage : user prefs
LocalStorageFlow --> ComponentStateCache : cmp state
LocalStorageFlow --> FormDraftStorage : drafts
LocalStorageFlow --> PostgreSQL : sync server

StateManagementFlow --> LocalStorage : state cache
StateManagementFlow --> Redis : state sync
StateManagementFlow --> PostgreSQL : state persist
StateManagementFlow --> Component : bind state

note right of PostgreSQL
  **Data access:**
  - read/write split
  - replication
  - sharding by project id
  - indexes
end note

note right of Redis
  **Caching:**
  - hot cache
  - sessions
  - collab state
  - TTL expiry
end note

note right of LocalStorage
  **Local storage:**
  - temp cache (auto purge)
  - user prefs (persisted)
  - component cache (session)
  - form drafts (TTL)
  - sync: incremental to server
end note

@enduml
